Some of these old numbers are just that, old. If they have a Sylvania
catalog at the flaps handy it will list Sylvania numbers by bulb location
for your model. I find these bulbs everywhere: large selection.

http://www.sylvania.com/bin/carApp/carApp_ver2.pl?flag=model_quals&make=&mak
e=Volkswagen&year=&year=1983&model=Vanagon&x=8&y=5

